OL,6,FA Belfast man who killed his friend
OL,7,Fclaiming he had been antagonised into
OL,8,Fpunching his victim was today handed a
OL,9,Fthree-and-a-half year prison sentence.
OL,10,FEdward Kelly, 31, formerly of Felt
OL,11,FStreet in the city, was told he will
OL,12,Fspend 21 months in custody followed by
OL,13,Fa similar period on licence after he
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to the manslaughter of
OL,15,FDavid Conville.JMr Conville, 34, died
OL,16,Fin the Royal Victoria Hospital in
OL,17,FBelfast three days after he was
OL,18,Fassaulted in the back garden of his
OL,19,Fsouth Belfast home almost two years
OL,20,Fago.
