OL,6,FBelfast Crown Court heard that Mr
OL,7,FConville was drinking with his
OL,8,Fgirlfriend when Kelly called at his
OL,9,FAbingdon Drive home off the Donegall
OL,10,FRoad on Friday, May 27, 2022.JAfter a
OL,11,Fconversation at the front door, Kelly
OL,12,Fleft but later returned half an hour
OL,13,Flater and the two men were seen in the
OL,14,Fback garden.JMr Conville's father told
OL,15,Fpolice he couldn't hear what was being
OL,16,Fsaid but "it didn't appear to be
OL,17,Fheated''.JThe victim's girlfriend said
OL,18,Fshe looked out the kitchen window and
OL,19,Fsaw her boyfriend "lying on the
OL,20,Fground'' at the back gate and went to
OL,21,Fhis aid.
