OL,6,FShe said Mr Conville was 6ft 2in tall,
OL,7,Fof medium build and weighing 91kg.
OL,8,FKelly was 5ft 7in tall, of slim build
OL,9,Fand weighing 63.5 kg.JMs McDermott
OL,10,Fsaid the incident was unplanned and
OL,11,Fthe defendant and the deceased were
OL,12,Ffriends before the assault.JJudge
OL,13,FDonna McColgan KC said she had
OL,14,Freceived two victim impact statements
OL,15,F- one from Mr Conville's sister and
OL,16,Fone from his former partner who he had
OL,17,Ftwo children with.JHis sister Lee-Anne
OL,18,FFerguson said: "Our lives were
OL,19,Fshattered on Friday, May 27, 2022, We
OL,20,Fhad a few very long days in the
OL,21,Fintensive care unit with no option but
OL,22,Fto watch as David's condition
OL,23,Fdeteriorated until he eventually
OL,24,Fpassed away.J"The grief we have all
OL,25,Ffelt is immeasurable. This pain was a
OL,26,Fwhole new level of grief and upset.''
