OL,6,FThe full statement from Lee-Anne
OL,7,FFerguson, David's sister, reads: "The
OL,8,FConville family would like to thank
OL,9,Feveryone for the kindness and support
OL,10,Fthey've given us since this horrific
OL,11,Fattack took place.J"David was at his
OL,12,Ffamily home, the very place he should
OL,13,Fhave felt safe. Instead he was
OL,14,Fattacked, outside the house, and later
OL,15,Fdied from the injuries sustained. He
OL,16,Fwas taken from us in the most cruel
OL,17,Fway.J"There are no words that describe
OL,18,Fthe loss we as a family have suffered
OL,19,Fand continue to suffer. David was only
OL,20,F34 years old.J"He was a devoted and
OL,21,Fmuch-loved dad, a loving son and
OL,22,Fbrother, and a friend to all.J"Not
OL,23,Fonly have we lost David, but just
OL,24,Feight months after he was killed, our
OL,25,Fmum died of a broken heart. The loss
OL,26,Fof her son was just too much to bear.
